hopobject.body: I'm unemployed tretinoin cream 0.05 costco Look at Tennessee, and you'll find the Titans with a 3-1 record before last week's game. That was WITH Jake Locker at QB. Locker did not suit up for last week's game, Ryan Fitzpatrick took over, and boom, the Titans lost to the Chiefs, 26-17. Just one more thing left to say, and that is, this IS my BEST BET BABY! Also like the Texans -7 points over the Rams, and we'll drop half a Benjamin on each game.
